<div class="alert gw-box" style="text-align: center; padding: 8px 15px; background-color: #e1e1e1;"><strong><a href="/wiki/Portage" title="Portage">Portage - the heart of Gentoo</a></strong><br /><a href="/wiki/Emerge" title="Emerge">emerge</a> ‚Äî <a class="mw-selflink selflink">configuration</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/Ebuild_repository" title="Ebuild repository">ebuild repository</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/Dispatch-conf" title="Dispatch-conf">dispatch-conf</a><br /><span class="mw-collapsible mw-collapsed"><br /><a href="/wiki/Selected-packages_set_(Portage)" title="Selected-packages set (Portage)">world file</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/USE_flag" title="USE flag">USE flags</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/Ebuild" title="Ebuild">ebuilds</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/Profile_(Portage)" title="Profile (Portage)">profiles</a> <br /><a href="/wiki/Upgrading_Gentoo" title="Upgrading Gentoo">upgrades</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/Knowledge_Base:Accepting_a_keyword_for_a_single_package" title="Knowledge Base:Accepting a keyword for a single package">using testing packages</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/Binary_package_guide" title="Binary package guide">binary packages</a><br /><a href="/wiki/Useful_Portage_tools" title="Useful Portage tools">tools</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/Gentoolkit" title="Gentoolkit">gentoolkit</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/Eselect" title="Eselect">eselect</a><br /><a href="/wiki/Project:Portage/FAQ" title="Project:Portage/FAQ">Portage FAQ</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/Gentoo_Cheat_Sheet" title="Gentoo Cheat Sheet">cheat sheet</a> ‚Äî <a href="/wiki/FAQ" title="FAQ">FAQ</a><br /><a href="/wiki/Category:Portage" title="Category:Portage">all articles</a><br /></span>
